        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[Cointelegraph 假新闻报告，轻信网友萤幕截图！SEC：小心网路上阅读的资讯]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="intro_quote">外媒 Cointelegraph 昨日一则假消息：「突发：SEC 核准 ishares 比特币现货 ETF」，让比特币瞬间上冲下洗，<a href="https://www.coinglass.com/LiquidationData" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Coinglass 数据</a>显示过去 24 小时内爆仓金额达 1.86 亿美元。对于如此离谱事情，Cointelegraph 于今早发布了调查报告，同时也引来了 SEC 的热心宣导。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_56_1 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/cointelegraph-fake-news-report#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-652e28f0f2b62"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-652e28f0f2b62"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/cointelegraph-fake-news-report/#Cointelegraph_%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%AA%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%A6%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%94%E6%80%A5%E6%96%BC%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83" title="Cointelegraph 事件调查报告：未证实来源真实性且急于发布">Cointelegraph 事件调查报告：未证实来源真实性且急于发布</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/cointelegraph-fake-news-report/#SEC%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83%E4%BD%A0%E5%9C%A8%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%B1%E8%AE%80%E7%9A%84%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A" title="SEC：小心你在网路上阅读的资讯">SEC：小心你在网路上阅读的资讯</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Cointelegraph_%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%AA%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%A6%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%94%E6%80%A5%E6%96%BC%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83"></span>Cointelegraph 事件调查报告：未证实来源真实性且急于发布<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>根据<a href="https://cointelegraph.com/news/clarification-sharing-false-spot-bitcoin-etf-news" target="_blank" rel="noopener">调查文章</a>，Cointelegraph 称其社群媒体团队在未经编辑事先批准的情况下在 X (Twitter) 上发布了消息，而该消息源自于一名 X 用户未经证实的萤幕截图，该用户声称截图来自彭博终端机。</p><p><img class="alignnone wp-image-80899 " src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2023-10-17-%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8811.00.20.png?resize=791%2C365&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="791" height="365" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-17-上午 11.00.20.png?w=1118&amp;ssl=1 1118w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-17-上午 11.00.20.png?resize=300%2C138&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-17-上午 11.00.20.png?resize=1024%2C473&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-17-上午 11.00.20.png?resize=600%2C277&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-17-上午 11.00.20.png?resize=768%2C354&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 791px) 100vw, 791px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>接著消息被传到某&nbsp;Telegram 群组，Cointelegraph 称其员工使用该频道来挖掘读者可能感兴趣的故事。在将该突发消息分享至 Cointelegraph 内部 Slack 后，为了加速发布速度，Cointelegraph 员工在未证实来源真实性的情况下便于 X 发布。</p><p>在 Cointelegraph 发现此消息可能为伪后，便将贴文内容进行了修改 (多加 Reportedly，「据报导、传闻」的意思)。接著 Cointelegraph 在从&nbsp;BlackRock 及彭博终端机得知消息并非属实后，才将贴文删除。</p><p><img class="alignnone wp-image-80901 " src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2023-10-17-%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8811.04.01.png?resize=878%2C457&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="878" height="457" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-17-上午 11.04.01.png?w=1132&amp;ssl=1 1132w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-17-上午 11.04.01.png?resize=300%2C156&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-17-上午 11.04.01.png?resize=1024%2C533&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-17-上午 11.04.01.png?resize=600%2C312&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-17-上午 11.04.01.png?resize=768%2C400&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 878px) 100vw, 878px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>对于此事，Cointelegraph 表示为了确保类似的事情不再发生，团队正彻底审查社群媒体管理流程，特别是在发布贴文之前对突发新闻的验证。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="SEC%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83%E4%BD%A0%E5%9C%A8%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%B1%E8%AE%80%E7%9A%84%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A"></span>SEC：小心你在网路上阅读的资讯<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 似乎也察觉到了 Cointelegraph 的假新闻对于市场的影响，于今日表示：「小心你在网路上阅读的资讯，关于 SEC 资讯最好的来源就是 SEC。」</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Careful what you read on the internet. The best source of information about the SEC is the SEC.</p><p>— U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (@SECGov) <a href="https://twitter.com/SECGov/status/1714020932509982771?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 16, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p>
]]>
            </description>
