        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[比特币 ETF 假消息来源？一则相同讯息早于 Cointelegraph 发布]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>「比特币市场庞大，所以无法被操弄？」10/16 晚间，一则媒体假新闻就让比特币上涨到 30K ; 很快被证实为假消息后，币价很快又回落 28K。链上侦探 ZachXBT 表示，来自媒体 Cointelegraph 的假消息，可能来自一则社群贴文。</p><figure id="attachment_80886" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-80886" style="width: 1698px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img class="wp-image-80886 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BTC_price-1.png?resize=1698%2C944&amp;ssl=1" alt="BTC_price" width="1698" height="944" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BTC_price-1.png?w=1698&amp;ssl=1 1698w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BTC_price-1.png?resize=300%2C167&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BTC_price-1.png?resize=1024%2C569&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BTC_price-1.png?resize=600%2C334&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BTC_price-1.png?resize=768%2C427&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BTC_price-1.png?resize=1536%2C854&amp;ssl=1 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption id="caption-attachment-80886" class="wp-caption-text">比特币因为假消息急上急下</figcaption></figure><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_56_1 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/fake-news-btc-spot-etf-pass#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-652e28f10db2f"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-652e28f10db2f"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/fake-news-btc-spot-etf-pass/#%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3_ETF_%E5%81%87%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%EF%BC%8CBTC_%E9%A3%86%E8%87%B3_30K" title="比特币 ETF 假消息，BTC 飙至 30K">比特币 ETF 假消息，BTC 飙至 30K</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/fake-news-btc-spot-etf-pass/#%E9%8F%88%E4%B8%8A%E5%81%B5%E6%8E%A2%EF%BC%9A%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF%E6%9B%B4%E6%97%A9%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%9C%A8%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4" title="链上侦探：相同讯息更早出现在社群">链上侦探：相同讯息更早出现在社群</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3" href="https://abmedia.io/fake-news-btc-spot-etf-pass/#10_%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%96%AA%E5%A4%B1%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%94%E8%90%AC%E9%8E%82%EF%BC%81%E5%B7%A8%E9%AF%A8%E5%9B%A0%E5%81%87%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1" title="10 分钟丧失近五万镁！巨鲸因假新闻损失">10 分钟丧失近五万镁！巨鲸因假新闻损失</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4" href="https://abmedia.io/fake-news-btc-spot-etf-pass/#%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%A4%E5%A0%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E" title="那些被误报的新闻">那些被误报的新闻</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3_ETF_%E5%81%87%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%EF%BC%8CBTC_%E9%A3%86%E8%87%B3_30K"></span>比特币 ETF 假消息，BTC 飙至 30K<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>9/16 晚间 21:21 媒体 Cointelegraph 推特发出：「突发：SEC 核准 ishares 比特币现货 ETF」，比特币因此强力上涨，甚至到达 30K。不过，很快的 BlackRock <a href="https://x.com/EleanorTerrett/status/1713913109272809602?s=20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">表示</a>这是错误消息，大力看好比特币现货 ETF 的<a href="https://x.com/JSeyff/status/1713911641555824732?s=20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">分析师</a>也都认为是这假新闻。比特币价格很快回落，媒体 Cointelegraph 也<a href="https://x.com/Cointelegraph/status/1713925876969017792?s=20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">公开致歉</a>，表示将尽快公布内部调查结果。</p><p><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-80887" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cointelegraph_fakenews.jpg?resize=600%2C371&amp;ssl=1" alt="cointelegraph_fakenews" width="600" height="371" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cointelegraph_fakenews.jpg?resize=600%2C371&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cointelegraph_fakenews.jpg?resize=300%2C186&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cointelegraph_fakenews.jpg?resize=1024%2C634&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cointelegraph_fakenews.jpg?resize=768%2C475&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cointelegraph_fakenews.jpg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E9%8F%88%E4%B8%8A%E5%81%B5%E6%8E%A2%EF%BC%9A%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF%E6%9B%B4%E6%97%A9%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%9C%A8%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4"></span>链上侦探：相同讯息更早出现在社群<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>链上侦探 ZachXBT 表示，媒体 Cointelegraph 的假消息，可能是抄了社群的传闻。早于 Cointelegraph 的假消息前，已经有相同文字出现在社群讨论中，当被发现是假消息后，已经删文。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">A user in this Telegram channel posted the exact same fake news reported by CoinTelegraph 39 minutes before their tweet.</p><p>After they deleted their message and account. <a href="https://t.co/CP98ex56ZU">pic.twitter.com/CP98ex56ZU</a></p><p>— ZachXBT (@zachxbt) <a href="https://twitter.com/zachxbt/status/1713949999476711883?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 16, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="10_%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%96%AA%E5%A4%B1%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%94%E8%90%AC%E9%8E%82%EF%BC%81%E5%B7%A8%E9%AF%A8%E5%9B%A0%E5%81%87%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1"></span>10 分钟丧失近五万镁！巨鲸因假新闻损失<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>Cointelegraph 推特帐号发出通过比特币现货 ETF 的假消息，导致链上巨鲸大额买入 61 万美金的比特币，在证实为假消息后，又以 56 万美金价值卖出。前后仅花了十分钟。</p><p class="p1">此外，据统计此次假新闻造成合约市场爆仓达 1 亿美元。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Cointelegraph’s fake news that the SEC approved iShares Bitcoin Spot <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/ETF?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#ETF</a> has caused many users to <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/FOMO?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#FOMO</a> and lose money.</p><p>A whale spent 613,201 <a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%24USDC&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">$USDC</a> to buy 20.5 <a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%24WBTC&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">$WBTC</a> and quickly sold for 563,970 <a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%24USDC&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">$USDC</a> after it was confirmed fake news.</p><p>The whale lost $49K in just 10 minutes! <a href="https://t.co/8YSPPjCvbr">pic.twitter.com/8YSPPjCvbr</a></p><p>— Lookonchain (@lookonchain) <a href="https://twitter.com/lookonchain/status/1713920641521660232?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 16, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%A4%E5%A0%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E"></span>那些被误报的新闻<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p><a href="https://abmedia.io/taiwan-crypto-media-make-up-taiwan-sec-news">误传「九月公布银行业买卖加密货币规范」，还原金管会质询现场</a></p><p><a href="https://abmedia.io/crypto-media-misunderstood-tax-arrears-case">误报「政府清查加密货币遗产税」，法务部执行署公文真相是？</a></p><p class="p1"><a href="https://t.me/abmedia_news/7354" target="_blank" rel="noopener">美国喜剧演员 Samuel Hyde 被媒体误认为 FTX 骇客</a></p><p><a href="https://abmedia.io/michael-burry-10m-put-misleading-news">媒体误报「大卖空主角 Michael Burry 买入 1000 万美元看跌期权」，考验读者识读能力</a></p><div id="gtx-trans" style="position: absolute; left: 173px; top: 2098.05px;"><div class="gtx-trans-icon">&nbsp;</div></div>
]]>
