            <title>
                <![CDATA[恶意帐号谣传 Solana 可手动停机！Solana 基金会：有 40 万美元赏金，欢迎去找]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Fyi there's a $400k reward for anyone that can find code that can turn off Solana</p><p>Please go ahead and find it<a href="https://t.co/2oxcB0EEyx">https://t.co/2oxcB0EEyx</a></p><p>— Jacob Creech (@jacobvcreech) <a href="https://twitter.com/jacobvcreech/status/1712612381740703896?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 12, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_56_1 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/solana-liquidation-rumor#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-652e28f11e030"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-652e28f11e030"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/solana-liquidation-rumor/#%E6%83%A1%E6%84%8F%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F%E6%95%A3%E6%92%AD_Solana_%E5%81%9C%E6%A9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%A6%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96" title="恶意帐号散播 Solana 停机不实言论">恶意帐号散播 Solana 停机不实言论</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/solana-liquidation-rumor/#%E5%81%9C%E6%A9%9F%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%80%EF%BC%9FSolana_%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD" title="停机已成过往？Solana 正常运作中">停机已成过往？Solana 正常运作中</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E6%83%A1%E6%84%8F%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F%E6%95%A3%E6%92%AD_Solana_%E5%81%9C%E6%A9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%A6%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96"></span>恶意帐号散播 Solana 停机不实言论<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>X (Twitter) 帐号 Inner City Press 在 SBF 受审期间分享了许多法庭上证人的言论，而在 SBF 律师 Mark Cohen 与 Alameda Research 前执行长 Caroline Ellison 的<a href="https://twitter.com/innercitypress/status/1712461930424631499" target="_blank" rel="noopener">发言纪录</a>中，有个恶意帐号 Awful Jesse 假扮成 Inner City Press 并发表<a href="https://twitter.com/awfuljesse/status/1712466734287086021" target="_blank" rel="noopener">不实言论</a>，以下为其言论：</p><ul><li>Cohen：Solana 曾是个中心化的代币吗？</li><li>Ellison：是的，Solana 是一条风投区块链，我们可以按照意愿将其打开或关闭。</li><li>Cohen：妳曾有需要将其关闭吗？</li><li>Ellison：有的，为了清算正在做多的用户。</li><li>Cohen：谁把 Solana 关了？</li><li>Ellison：FTX 开发者们。</li></ul><p>此言论曝光后，被假消息骗到的群众在加密社群中大量分享此消息，该则贴文至今已超过 800 次转贴并近 1,500 个爱心。相较于 Inner City Press 的其他贴文，这则假消息可说是被传播的最快速也被最多人看到的。</p><p>Solana 基金会的开发者关系长 Jacob Creech 在看到此现象后，似乎是想表达该言论有多荒唐般，表示 Solana 基金会设有 40 万美元的赏金，只要有人能找到能将 Solana 关闭的程式码。</p><p><img class="alignnone wp-image-80872 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2023-10-16-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%885.06.56.png?resize=1311%2C233&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="1311" height="233" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-16-下午 5.06.56.png?w=1311&amp;ssl=1 1311w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-16-下午 5.06.56.png?resize=300%2C53&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-16-下午 5.06.56.png?resize=1024%2C182&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-16-下午 5.06.56.png?resize=600%2C107&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-16-下午 5.06.56.png?resize=768%2C136&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E5%81%9C%E6%A9%9F%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%80%EF%BC%9FSolana_%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD"></span>停机已成过往？Solana 正常运作中<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>恶意帐号 Awful Jesse 之所以会有此言论，无疑是想要抨击 Solana 自去年至今年初多次停机的现象，再加上 SBF 与 Solana 生态系的亲密关系，在 FTX 倒闭后也在一定程度上为 Solana 带来负面形象。</p><p>根据 DeFiLlama 的<a href="https://defillama.com/chain/Solana" target="_blank" rel="noopener">数据</a>，在去年 11 月后 Solana 的 TVL 急剧下跌，目前约维持在 3 亿美元左右。不过根据 Solana 官网的<a href="https://status.solana.com/history?page=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">事故报告</a>，Solana 自今年 2 月后便未出现停机现象，已正常运行超过 8 个月。</p>
]]>
            </description>
